{"tid":2158154,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"30:49 戴耀廷點睇入唔入非法立法會,   有 point, 大家可以聽下.","createTime":"2020-08-15T13:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T15:18:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7df60e06a62c13fa50d77bd5e9b41ab2d94a9a0f","tid":2158154,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"30:49<br />\n戴耀廷點睇入唔入非法立法會,   有 point, 大家可以聽下.<br />\n<br />\n戴耀廷拆局！中共人大新招立法會延任 民主派進退兩難 拉撒路計劃新進展（D100 上兵伐謀）戴耀廷，陳珏明<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LUI2frSNfRg?t=1849\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLUI2frSNfRg%3Ft%3D1849&d=Z4osEZd2TI9THLKNWu9EL%2FzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=9db75236\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LUI2frSNfRg?t=1849</a>"},{"pid":"13ebde1b27b6a025eeb31b878c4a7fcf70264cd9","tid":2158154,"uid":283764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:46:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb06bce96d71d90ab194a1ceb1c2727e2244b9fb","tid":2158154,"uid":275384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T16:57:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50838cbecdf0bfa81fda6c20010fc48001074e16","tid":2158154,"uid":249979,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T05:19:40.000Z","msg":"所有泛民都應該杯葛立會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 杯葛立會使其失去合法性，區選已證明大多數人支持泛民。<br />\n2. 人民授權4年期限已到，臨時立會有人民授權係歪理。<br />\n3. 人大委任是非法，國際亦認同，泛民不應配合中央歪曲基本法。<br />\n4. 留守立會抗爭空間已不存在，聯合區議員成立「影子議會」議政。<br />\n5. 為下屆選舉爭取籌碼，如果下屆再DQ議員，泛民繼續杯葛。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">6. 北京明顯派人放風希望泛民參加，如果泛民唔參加，等同開綠燈比美國制裁臨時立會議員、香港政府必定迎來更激烈嘅制裁。</span>"},{"pid":"bb7eb1be97927e6f826b47cdf85fa3d1996faa30","tid":2158154,"uid":58266,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T09:46:09.000Z","msg":"呢個概念同運動初期，不分化，各自努力，一致。"},{"pid":"ceb888c6d0a48c15038e33942ad809073448fcf4","tid":2158154,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb7eb1be97927e6f826b47cdf85fa3d1996faa3